# Anchorpipe Performance & Theming

- Entry bundle <100KB gz; enforce route-level code splitting; remove unused deps.
- RSC-first, Suspense/streaming; prefetch sensibly; cache via ISR/ETag where applicable.
- Responsive: fluid typography, responsive spacing, responsive images.
- Themes: light/dark/high-contrast parity; no contrast regressions when switching.
